  "detailed_description": "A precision-based puzzle game about dashing in the world of polygons.<br><br>Jump between obstacles, avoid spikes, reflect from obstacles, use portals and unlock gates to achieve your goal - collect all the coins on the board.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\t<li> 50 hand-crafted levels full of dashing, dying, reflecting and teleporting<br>\t</li><li> pass every level in any way you want - no time pressure<br>\t</li><li> undo your moves when you are stuck<br>\t</li><li> challenge yourself by completing levels with Perfect Pass status (collect at least one coin in each dash)<br>\t</li><li> listen to relaxing music<br>        </li><li> unlock 50 achievements</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dash + Collect</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/5c02c00d06b21944c14666578eb2f261.poster.avif?t=1681662387\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/5c02c00d06b21944c14666578eb2f261.webm?t=1681662387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/5c02c00d06b21944c14666578eb2f261.mp4?t=1681662387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid Spikes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/9775cc56121f34572dbe0faea2904a0f.poster.avif?t=1681662387\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/9775cc56121f34572dbe0faea2904a0f.webm?t=1681662387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678100/extras/9775cc56121f34572dbe0faea2904a0f.mp4?t=1